name: Melevate
bio:
Melevate is a dynamic local DJ from San Francisco. Her signature style encompasses genres like progressive house, melodic techno, and trance. With a passion for music and an innate talent for turning tunes into experiences, her curation and blending of these genres create an electrifying soundscape, guiding her audience on a thrilling sonic voyage to new heights of musical ecstasy.





Melevate has performed at iconic venues such as Halcyon, 1015 Folsom, Audio, Hawthorn, Bergerac, Phoenix Hotel, and many more. Sheâ€™s shared the stage with Oliver Smith, Tita Lau, TokiMonsta, Audien, ZOYA, Return of the Jaded, JOPLYN, Robin Schulz, and Jordan Suckley. She's also been featured on the LA radio show/podcast, Global Dance Mission, allowing her music to reach a worldwide audience.
